"     The airway management algorithms cited in this review are reproduced with permission from: The Difficult Airway Course&trade;: Emergency, and Walls, RM, Murphy, MF. Manual of Emergency Airway Management, 4th ed, Lippincott Williams &amp; Wilkins, Philadelphia 2012.",
